{"tid":1077427,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阮兆祥離開TVB：練咗功夫咁耐想闖下","createTime":"2019-03-25T14:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T03:01:22.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ee27f652ae82dcfe334d2ea7c3518db7f830fc83","tid":1077427,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"阮兆祥約滿TVB離開，加盟王祖藍公司成旗下藝人。今晚祥仔現身活動，表示效力TVB 30年，感謝舊公司栽培，讓他有好多練習機會。他說早於去年底醞釀離巢，公司高層挽留但他最後決定離開。他說：「去留問題想了很久，我練了功夫好耐，想闖一下，我想轉換下新環境，不過地球是圓的，不排除將來再合作，今年我有計劃再出唱片，始終自己做歌手出身，幾十年無出唱片，最近忙於搵人寫歌，籌備拍MV，想舖排10月去麥花臣開個唱，對我來講好大挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190324/1553428062130/【又走一個】阮兆祥離開tvb-練咗功夫咁耐想闖下\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190324%2F1553428062130%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8F%88%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E3%80%91%E9%98%AE%E5%85%86%E7%A5%A5%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8Btvb-%E7%B7%B4%E5%92%97%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%E5%92%81%E8%80%90%E6%83%B3%E9%97%96%E4%B8%8B&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq1DApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=8c074221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190324%2F1553428062130%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8F%88%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E3%80%91%E9%98%AE%E5%85%86%E7%A5%A5%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8Btvb-%E7%B7%B4%E5%92%97%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%E5%92%81%E8%80%90%E6%83%B3%E9%97%96%E4%B8%8B&h=69d1d5cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190324/1553428062130/【又走一個】阮兆祥離開tvb-練咗功夫咁耐想闖下</a>"},{"pid":"2b488e941547876a9660360957df1ae1a25bbb24","tid":1077427,"uid":167566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:46:23.000Z","msg":"Hahaha"},{"pid":"d0c3fe41bcd7a44e460587de81b45a764e8c93f6","tid":1077427,"uid":41343,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"出左去真係唔知淥死誰手"},{"pid":"a5521d6eba7a8a91ba8ddef8b8b753ad43e69cb3","tid":1077427,"uid":145927,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c3fe